700497f-a.title: Bronx: Benson Street - St. Raymond Avenue
700497f-a.text:
(1)
Benson Street, west side, between St. Raymond Ave. and Maclay
Ave.,  showing the north side of an old house as seen from Maclay Ave.
August 3, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
A view of the south side of the house as seen from Benson
Street, at a later date.
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
